==Ugaritic==
===Etymology===
From Proto-Semitic.
===Pronunciation===
Reconstructed as */ʔayyal-u/ (in nominative singular).
===Noun===
'''ảyl''', {{m}}, {{p}} ''ảylm''.
# A [[red deer]].
#:''tṭbḫ šb`m ảylm'', she slew seventy harts.
# A [[hart]] or [[stag]] - a male red deer, as opposed to [[ảylt]].
===Synonyms===
*[[Cervus elaphus]] ''Scientific name''
===Related terms===
* ''[[ảylt]]'' (fem.)

